<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̹n knt mdywn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̹n knt mdywn wạldẖnb kbyr
 wʿạyz ạlạ̉mạn wrạḥẗ ạlḍmyr
 tʿạla lyswʿ dạ ḥbh kbyr
 dạ ḥml ạlậtẖạm wạldyn ạlkẖṭyr
 ạlqrạr- hygẖyrk wyḥrrk mn kl qyd
 wyfrḥk wysndk bạlmwạʿyd
 2- ạ̹n knt tʿbạn wạlqlb jryḥ
 wʿạyz ạlḥbyb wạlḥb ạlṣḥyḥ
 tʿạla lyswʿ dạ ḥbh ṣryḥ
 dạ mạt bạlṣlyb wkạn ạldẖbyḥ</lyrics>
<author>ạ̹yfwn kẖạld, ạ̹yfwn kẖạld</author>
<hymn_number>9692</hymn_number>
</song>